"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-news-world-paris-olympics-la-defense-arena-sustainability-b1160587.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the search feature\", \"from\": 7, \"to\": 25}, {\"ngram\": \"your consent\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 47}, {\"ngram\": \"cookies\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"similar technologies\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our privacy policy\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 205}, {\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"News|World Paris La D\\u00e9fense Arena is not your typicalOlympicand Paralympic swimming venue.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris La D\\u00e9fense Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\"}, {\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For one thing, there is currently no water.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"no water\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moreover, until recently, the area where the pool must go was plastered with dozens of trucks and sparkly sequins, dismantling the set ofTaylor Swift's Eras Tour, whose European leg kicked off in Parisearlier this month.\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Gehrels_Swift_Observatory\", \"score\": 0.6650400132345805, \"rank\": 0.5034436515064102, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q2133344\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Gehrels_Swift_Observatory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Gehrels_Swift_Observatory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"trucks\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"sparkly sequins\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"whose European leg\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisearlier\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet within hours, both the hardware and glitter had gone.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"both the hardware\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"glitter\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks to its modular and multi-purpose structure, the arena - which first opened its doors in 2017 and was designed by architect Christian de Portzamparc - will soon be host to an Olympic-sized swimming pool and warm-up areas, as if Taylor (or the rugby pitch belonging to Racing 92, its resident club) never existed.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its modular and multi-purpose structure\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"its doors\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"architect Christian de Portzamparc\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"host\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic-sized swimming pool\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"warm-up areas\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"Taylor\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"the rugby pitch\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"its resident club\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is difficult to describe the arena's scale but let me try.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the arena's scale\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is Europe's largest indoor venue, capable of hosting up to 45,000 people.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe's largest indoor venue\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"45,000 people\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is home to the world's largest interactive giant screen, with 1,400 square metres worth of display area, equivalent to seven tennis courts.\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's largest interactive giant screen\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"1,400 square metres\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"display area\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"seven tennis courts\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its roof can handle 250 tonnes of weight.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its roof\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"250 tonnes\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The history of theOlympic Gameshas all too often been one of cost overruns and white elephants.Paris 2024wants to change all that - an impressive 95 per cent of its Olympic venues are existing or temporary, which is vital for an event with sustainability at its heart.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The history\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Gameshas\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"cost overruns\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"white elephants\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"an impressive 95 per cent\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"its Olympic venues\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"its heart\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this way, Paris La D\\u00e9fense Arena is a worthy venue which has incorporated energy efficiency and sustainability into its development from the very beginning.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris La D\\u00e9fense Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this way\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"a worthy venue\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"energy efficiency\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"its development\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the very beginning\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than traditional (and energy-intensive) heating and air conditioning systems, the facility relies upon high-performance thermal and acoustic insulation, which can ensure uniform temperatures regardless of outdoor weather conditions.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"traditional (and energy-intensive) heating and air conditioning systems\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"the facility\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"high-performance thermal and acoustic insulation\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"uniform temperatures\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"outdoor weather conditions\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, any collected rainwater funnels into an 800m\\u00b3 storage tank located beneath the underground car park.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"an 800m\\u00b3 storage tank\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"the underground car park\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This water provides 100 per cent of the lawn irrigation needs.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This water\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"100 per cent\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"the lawn irrigation needs\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, solar panels on the roof are used to power the adjoining brewery.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"solar panels\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"the roof\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"the adjoining brewery\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The arena's waste management policy is also impressive.\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The arena's waste management policy\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since May 2022, it has established its own on-site waste sorting centre.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"site\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By 2025, it aims for an 80 per cent recycling rate and 40 per cent energy reduction.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an 80 per cent recycling rate\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"40 per cent energy reduction\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If it's good enough for Taylor and around 180,000 Swifties, it should work for the Olympics and Paralympics.\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Taylor\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2461}, {\"ngram\": \"around 180,000 Swifties\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2489}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 202